usage: fritzbox-forward-port (ENABLE|DISABLE) DESTINATION_IP PORT [COMMENT]
       fritzbox-forward-port --help

    This script will enable/disable port $PORT forwarding on
    a FRITZ!Box to the $DESTINATION_IP

     You can set the following variables directly in the
     script, or in `~/.fritzbox.conf` :

         FB=fritz.box
         FB_USER=fritz1234
         FB_PASS=password
         FB_CERT=~/.fritzbox.pem

     FB_CERT can be left empty but then the https
     connection will NOT be authenticated

